<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="5Aug1940"><font color="red">5 August 1940</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Ben Huebsch): cable to me at the U.S. embassy in Vichy through the State Department at Washington whatever sum &hellip; British subjects &hellip; are under the protection of the U.S. embassy &hellip; Mr Robert Murphy, acting charg&eacute; d&apos;affaires in the absence of Mr William Bullitt, received me the other day in Vichy </div>
